== Romanian ==
=== Etymology ===
Pre-Roman. Probably via [[W:Dacian language|Dacian]] from [[PIE]] *bhereg-, "white". The Romanian word has a [[cognate]] in [[W:Albanian language|Albanian]], ''[[bardhë]]'', "white".
===Noun===
'''barză''' pl ''[[berze]]''
#[[stork]].

